{"tid":160403,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"「技能相換」+「活動自組」","createTime":"2017-03-17T16:24:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-28T17:27:17.000Z","uid":74954,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"55cd59dd044e15d8cfef8ff5fe44b8b12b652910","tid":160403,"uid":74954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T16:24:14.000Z","msg":"眼見各巴打都希望學新野<br />\n同希望組團成人 所以提供集中d既平台比大家免費使用<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n各位巴打 <br />\n如果想交換技能學習<br />\n又唔想爬post 看<br />\n想方便d 預約 報名 交換 有confirmed email <br />\n我地提供免費平台俾大家用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大家可以登自己既興趣上去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同想接收咩技能<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.multiplatic.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.multiplatic.com&d=eFPPjfgCRbiAcgLUcX%2Bp1TCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=d4784e28\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.multiplatic.com</a><br />\n<br />\n我地仲有提供自組活動<br />\n如果一個毒L想去玩/想去旅行/想學興趣班/想玩board game/想打麻雀等等無人陪 或者唔夠腳<br />\n都可以係我地到post 活動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n希望提供一個集中嘅活動興趣技能平台俾大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n已經有活動可以搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有興趣可以試下用<br />\n我地仲有個blog 比大家討論<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.multiplatic.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.multiplatic.com&d=eFPPjfgCRbiAcgLUcX%2Bp1TCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=d4784e28\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.multiplatic.com</a>"},{"pid":"84db11d6885e6722b133955117937dd076668de1","tid":160403,"uid":74954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T16:30:55.000Z","msg":"另外 如果我地見技能相換既反應熱烈既話<br />\n我地會搞一個Convention <br />\n希望到時可以有個場地互相分享<img src=